PN,36801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FAfter a funeral director pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to 67 charges relating to the
OL,8,Fmishandling of bodies in his care,
OL,9,Fsome of the affected families have
OL,10,Fshared their experiences
OL,12,FKatie Woolston is no stranger to grief.
OL,14,FHaving been through multiple
OL,15,Fmiscarriages, she has become
OL,16,Faccustomed to coping with loss.
OL,18,FBut her dealings with Robert Bush and
OL,19,FLegacy Funeral Directors have, she
OL,20,Fsays, compounded her heartbreak.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,F"It's awful enough when you lose
OL,7,Fsomebody and you just want them to be
OL,8,Fable to rest peacefully," she says.
OL,9,F"To have all of this afterwards is
OL,10,Funimaginable."
OL,12,FKatie's family had used Legacy
OL,13,Fpreviously, when her grandparents died.
OL,15,FWhen Katie asked Bush to cremate her
OL,16,Fbaby's remains after suffering a third
OL,17,Fmiscarriage, she described the process
OL,18,Fas "plain sailing" and said she
OL,19,Freceived the ashes in a "presentable
OL,20,Fbox".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FBut when she went to him again after
OL,7,Fmiscarrying for a fourth time in 2023,
OL,8,Fthe experience felt different.
OL,10,F"When we picked the ashes up, they
OL,11,Fwere in a small box that I'd say you'd
OL,12,Freceive a parcel in," she said.
OL,14,F"I'd never dream of receiving ashes in
OL,15,Fthis box, the type of box it was. So I
OL,16,Fwas upset about that."
OL,18,FBut the situation would get much worse.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FWhen it was announced that Legacy was
OL,7,Funder investigation in March 2024,
OL,8,FKatie naturally wanted to know if she
OL,9,Fhad cause to be worried.
OL,11,FShe was initially told it was
OL,12,Fimpossible to say whether she had the
OL,13,Fright ashes because of the difficulty
OL,14,Fof DNA testing the remains.
OL,16,FBut investigations revealed Bush had
OL,17,Fgone to hospital to pick up her baby's
OL,18,Fbody on the same day he told the
OL,19,Ffamily the ashes could be collected -
OL,20,Fa logistical impossibility.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FKatie said: "I was told that (police)
OL,7,Fhad been to other crematoriums in the
OL,8,Farea and that there was no record of
OL,9,Fhim ever taking the remains to get
OL,10,Fcremated.
OL,12,F"So that obviously meant that the
OL,13,Fashes weren't our baby's remains.
OL,15,F"It was awful. At the time when the
OL,16,Fpolice came to tell me this, I was
OL,17,Fpregnant with our daughter Betsy,
OL,18,Fwhich was obviously already a
OL,19,Fstressful pregnancy after having four
OL,20,Fmiscarriages.
OL,26,@nD@^pmnD@epn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,F"I was already terrified that I would
OL,7,Flose Betsy while I was pregnant. So to
OL,8,Fadd more stress and worry and
OL,9,Feverything else onto that pregnancy -
OL,10,Fit was just heartbreaking."
OL,12,FThe uncertainty about what happened to
OL,13,Fher baby continues to haunt Katie
OL,14,Fthree years later.
OL,16,F"All I can think that he has done with
OL,17,Fthe baby's remains is just put them in
OL,18,Fa bin," she said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,F"That's the only way I can think what
OL,7,Fhe could have done with them, because
OL,8,Fthere's no evidence that they ever
OL,9,Fwent to a crematorium.
OL,11,F"There's nothing to tell me where my
OL,12,Fbaby's remains ended up. It's
OL,13,Ftorturous really, to sit and think
OL,14,Fabout where they could be or what he
OL,15,Fdid with them. It's horrible."
OL,17,FKatie's experience is mirrored by
OL,18,Fthree other sets of parents lied to by
OL,19,FBush about their babies' remains.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FShe has since returned the ashes she
OL,7,Fwas given to police, to form part of a
OL,8,Fmemorial garden opened for families
OL,9,Faffected by the scandal.
OL,11,FKatie said: "It was important to me to
OL,12,Fmake sure that these ashes, whoever
OL,13,Fthey are, are kind of looked after.
OL,14,FThey were in our house for a number of
OL,15,Fmonths and they were loved and cared
OL,16,Ffor while they were at our home.
OL,18,F"And now whoever's they are, they'll
OL,19,Fbe able to go and pay their respects
OL,20,Fand remember."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FLike many others, Katie is now calling
OL,7,Ffor strict regulation of the funeral
OL,8,Findustry.
OL,10,F"I just hope that nobody else ever
OL,11,Fdoes anything like this to anybody,"
OL,12,Fshe said.
OL,14,F"I hope that there is regulation and
OL,15,Fpeople can have their minds put at
OL,16,Fease, that when they give a funeral
OL,17,Fdirector their relative's body or
OL,18,Fremains that they'll be treated with
OL,19,Frespect and dignity."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,F'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,7,Fin a paper bag'
OL,9,FLike Katie, Jasmine Beverley had
OL,10,Fpreviously used Legacy for family
OL,11,Ffuneral arrangements.
OL,13,FShe described Robert Bush as a "nice
OL,14,Fguy". So when her son, Sunny Beverley-
OL,15,FConlin, was stillborn in 2022, Jasmine
OL,16,Fhad no reservations about entrusting
OL,17,Fhis cremation to the company.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FShe and her husband, Ben Conlin, kept
OL,7,Fan urn containing what they thought
OL,8,Fwere Sunny's ashes until news of the
OL,9,Fscandal broke almost two years later.
OL,11,FAnd then they received the worst
OL,12,Fpossible news.
OL,14,F"The police came and they told us that
OL,15,Fthey believed that Sunny had been
OL,16,Ffound in Legacy, and that the ashes
OL,17,Fthat we received were not Sunny,"
OL,18,FJasmine said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,F"It was really difficult to hear that
OL,7,Fbecause it had been two years since we
OL,8,Flost Sunny. And the thought of him
OL,9,Fbeing in (Legacy's building) was
OL,10,Freally difficult."
OL,12,FBush later pleaded guilty to fraud in
OL,13,Frelation to Jasmine's case but,
OL,14,Fbecause she lost Sunny less than 24
OL,15,Fweeks into pregnancy - the point at
OL,16,Fwhich life is deemed viable - Bush
OL,17,Favoided more serious charges.
OL,19,FJasmine now wants the law changed to
OL,20,Fgive greater recognition in similar
OL,21,Fcases.
OL,26,@qD@JpmqD@\pn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FShe said: "I want something to
OL,7,Frecognise that if you trust somebody
OL,8,Fto take care of your child who's dead
OL,9,Fpre-24 weeks, that there's some law in
OL,10,Fplace to say that that is what you
OL,11,Fmust do. You must respect and give
OL,12,Fdignity to the family's wishes.
OL,14,F"Sunny got no dignity. He was found on
OL,15,Fthe floor in a brown paper bag. To me,
OL,16,Fthat's not dignity. No crime has been
OL,17,Fcommitted, but to me that is a crime.
OL,18,FThat was a human being, that was my
OL,19,Fson, that was somebody that I loved."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G13/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FJasmine said there have been "moments"
OL,7,Fsince the investigation into Legacy
OL,8,Fstarted when she wanted to "forgive"
OL,9,FRobert Bush.
OL,11,F"In this moment, I don't want to
OL,12,Fforgive him," she added. "I don't
OL,13,Fthink I need to forgive him right now.
OL,14,FI just want him to be punished for
OL,15,Fwhat he's done as much as the law will
OL,16,Fallow.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G14/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,F"If he shows some sort of remorse to
OL,7,Fwhat he's done, then maybe I could
OL,8,Fslowly start to, I don't know if
OL,9,F'forgive' is the right word even, but
OL,10,Fslowly start to understand where he's
OL,11,Fcome from. Because forgiveness is
OL,12,Fearned, and what he's done to so many
OL,13,Fof us is difficult to move on from."
OL,15,F'We had someone else's ashes for two
OL,16,Fyears'
OL,18,FTracy Hudson's mother Sandra Kendall
OL,19,Fdied in 2021. For eight years, Tracy
OL,20,Flooked after her mother through
OL,21,FAlzheimer's and vascular dementia.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G15/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FBut, following her funeral, it took
OL,7,Fanother six months - and constant
OL,8,Fexcuses from Legacy - before her
OL,9,Ffamily received what they thought were
OL,10,Fthe ashes.
OL,12,FTracy used part of the remains to have
OL,13,Fa ring made, allowing her to carry her
OL,14,Fmum with her wherever she went.
OL,16,FIt was another two years before news
OL,17,Fof the investigation into Legacy broke.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G16/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FTracy said: "I said to my husband, 'I
OL,7,Fthink I'll just ring (the police)',
OL,8,Fjust as a precaution really. So I did.
OL,9,FI didn't hear anything for a couple of
OL,10,Fweeks, so obviously at that point I
OL,11,Fthought my mother's not involved.
OL,13,F"But then I got a phone call at 10.30
OL,14,Fat night - I can't forget that time -
OL,15,Fand the police informed me that they
OL,16,Fhad found my mother's certificate and
OL,17,Fashes and everything to do with her...
OL,18,Ftwo and a half years after we lost my
OL,19,Fmother. And we'd had ashes prior to
OL,20,Fthat, which was not her."
OL,26,@oD@VpmoD@apn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G17/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36818
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FThe revelation was traumatising.
OL,8,F"I was distraught," Tracy said.
OL,10,F"I was very angry. We thought we did
OL,11,Feverything right for her, what she
OL,12,Fwanted for her funeral, everything.
OL,13,FAnd then to have this happen, it
OL,14,Fshattered everything.
OL,16,F"And we felt guilty. We felt we'd let
OL,17,Fmy mother down. And that guilt just
OL,18,Fdoesn't go away."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G18/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36819
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FShe said she had to give up her work
OL,7,Fwith children in schools and has been
OL,8,Fthrough counselling.
OL,10,F"How could anybody even think about
OL,11,Fbeing disrespectful in such a hideous
OL,12,Fway?" she said.
OL,14,F"You can't get your head around it. I
OL,15,Flove my mother, and I'll love her
OL,16,Funtil I'm with her again. And it
OL,17,Fdestroyed a lot in our family. My dad
OL,18,Fparticularly, and my brother. The pain
OL,19,Fwill never go away. Even justice, I
OL,20,Fdon't think will change it really."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G19/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36820
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FLike Katie, Tracy now wants the
OL,7,Ffuneral industry monitored.
OL,9,FBut, two-and-a-half years after her
OL,10,Fmother's death, she still has
OL,11,Fquestions of Robert Bush, a man she
OL,12,Fdescribes as a "monster".
OL,14,F"Why did you leave my mother? Why did
OL,15,Fyou give us the wrong ashes? Why was
OL,16,Fit two-and-a-half years before we knew
OL,17,Fmy mother was left on Hessle Road with
OL,18,Fthe other deceased people? Why?
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G20/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36821
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,F"We need an answer, and I think we
OL,7,Fdeserve an answer. I have a right of
OL,8,Fan answer. I have a right to be told
OL,9,Fwhy you did what you did to my mother."
OL,11,FInsight by ITV News reporter Vicki
OL,12,FSmith
OL,14,FIt's hard to comprehend the scale of
OL,15,Fhurt forced upon so many people in
OL,16,Fthis one part of the world, by one man.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G21/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36822
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FThe three women I spoke to all live
OL,7,Fwithin a few miles of each other in
OL,8,FHull. All have very personal stories
OL,9,Fof deep loss, grief and heartbreak.
OL,10,FBut now, they are all linked by the
OL,11,Fbetrayal they went through while in
OL,12,Fthe midst of grief.
OL,14,FFrom mothers to unborn children, their
OL,15,Floved ones were robbed of dignity and
OL,16,Fpeace.
OL,18,FI have spoken to many people affected
OL,19,Fby this case. Not all wanted to appear
OL,20,Fon camera or have their stories shared
OL,21,Fpublicly.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G22/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36823
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FFor many, what happened to them is the
OL,7,Fworst thing that they have ever been
OL,8,Fthrough and it continues to affect
OL,9,Ftheir lives and mental health.
OL,11,FMany talk of trusting Bush with their
OL,12,Ffamily members after he had dealt with
OL,13,Fother relatives' funerals. Many talk
OL,14,Fof a man who seemed like he wanted to
OL,15,Fhelp. What they are left with is the
OL,16,Fcruellest form of deceit.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G23/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36824
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775477468
OL,3,C'My baby's body was found on the floor
OL,4,Cin a paper bag'
OL,6,FA trial no longer being on the horizon
OL,7,Fis met with a real mix of feelings. It
OL,8,Fhas already been two years since the
OL,9,Finvestigation was launched and some
OL,10,Fwould welcome some form of closure.
OL,11,FOthers feel they are left with too
OL,12,Fmany unanswered questions. Why did he
OL,13,Fdo this? Or how was it allowed to
OL,14,Fhappen?
OL,16,FWhatever happens next in court, the
OL,17,Fvast majority of people affected want
OL,18,Fto see nationwide change so this can
OL,19,Fnever happen to another loved one,
OL,20,Fanother family, another city again.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G24/25
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
